<title>USA: Price Comms to buy Palmer Wireless.</title>
<headline>Price Comms to buy Palmer Wireless.</headline>
<dateline>FT. MYERS, Fla. 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Price Communications Corp has reached a definitive agreement to acquire Palmer Wireless Inc for $17.50 cash per share, for an aggregate purchase price of $880 million, including repayment of debt, Palmer said Friday.</p>
<p>Palmer said it expects the transaction to close in the fourth quarter.</p>
